sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  box rgb(255,242,204) Durable authority boundary
    participant Authority as Definition and image authority
  end
  box rgb(220,236,255) Trusted Cell host
    participant Cell
  end
  box rgb(238,229,247) Isolated Chamber
    participant Chamber
    participant Adapter as Language adapter
    participant Core as Primitive core
  end
  box rgb(255,228,220) Authored behavior
    participant Task as Business task
  end

  Authority->>Cell: Exact signed assignment, image and source-slice digests
  Cell->>Cell: Verify current generation, policy and containment measurement
  Cell->>Chamber: Launch measured runtime and transfer fixed descriptors
  Chamber->>Authority: Read through literal capability facade
  Authority-->>Chamber: Serialized definition authority
  Chamber->>Adapter: Materialize controlled callable source
  Adapter-->>Chamber: Callable or normalized materialization failure
  Chamber->>Core: Materialize primitive from definition plus callable
  Core->>Task: Execute governed handler
  Task-->>Core: Business context or domain failure
  Core-->>Chamber: Normalized primitive outcome and evidence
  Chamber-->>Cell: Result plus execution-custody barrier
  Note over Authority,Task: Core never evaluates callable source and business context never receives host credentials.
